<slide id="pYQ"><style><fill id="fYQ"><fillColor color="rgba(244, 244, 243, 1)"/></fill></style><data><shape width="960" height="540" topLeftX="0" topLeftY="0" type="rect" id="bbt"><fill><fillImg src="D7m2bdqoxobkHkxhpILlXRbxgIg" alpha="1" rotateWithShape="true" stretchLeft="0" stretchBottom="0" stretchRight="0" stretchTop="0"/></fill><content paddingTop="3.6" paddingBottom="3.6" paddingLeft="7.2" paddingRight="7.2" fontSize="16" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(31, 35, 41, 1)"><p textAlign="center" lineSpacing="multiple:1.2"><span color="rgba(255, 255, 255, 1)" fontSize="14" fontFamily="Arial" bold="false" italic="false" strikethrough="false" underline="false"> </span></p></content></shape><img id="bbg" src="W1i6bWATgooCNtxo4e3lGx1Eg6c" width="180" height="108" topLeftX="710" topLeftY="396"><crop leftOffset="0" rightOffset="0" topOffset="0" bottomOffset="0"/></img><img id="bbn" src="BNqEbXWrHoiP9lxc84Ul9Hhmgzh" width="86.52228346456693" height="11.42259842519685" topLeftX="649.334094488189" topLeftY="7.989291338582677"><crop leftOffset="0" rightOffset="0" topOffset="0" bottomOffset="0"/></img><shape width="118.11023622047244" height="30" topLeftX="641.3333070866141" topLeftY="510.92913385826773" type="text" id="bbd"><content paddingTop="10" paddingBottom="10" paddingLeft="10" paddingRight="10" fontSize="10" fontFamily="Space Grotesk Light" color="rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)" bold="false" italic="false" underline="false" strikethrough="false" lineSpacing="multiple:1.0" textAlign="left"/></shape><shape width="898" height="22" topLeftX="31.065590551181117" topLeftY="23.6115748031496" type="text" id="bbN"><content fontSize="24" fontFamily="Space Mono" color="rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)" bold="true" italic="false" underline="false" strikethrough="false" lineSpacing="multiple:0.9" textAlign="left"><p><strong><span fontSize="24">上半年总结与下半年规划</span></strong></p></content></shape><shape width="404" height="57" topLeftX="51.55097533847942" topLeftY="103.1065310647932" type="text" id="bbv"><fill><fillColor color="rgba(239, 239, 239, 1)"/></fill><border color="rgba(217, 217, 217, 1)" lineJoin="miter" miterLimit="10"/><content textType="sub-headline" fontSize="12" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(31, 35, 41, 1)" bold="true" textAlign="center" autoFit="shape-auto-fit"><p textAlign="center"><span fontSize="14">H1（上半年）</span></p><p textAlign="center"><span fontSize="12">还历史欠账，完成底层重构，实现从“能用”到“安全、可扩展”的跨越，为业务发展筑牢坚实的技术根基。</span></p></content></shape><shape width="404" height="57" topLeftX="495.28970887188655" topLeftY="104.77035433070874" type="text" id="bbM"><fill><fillColor color="rgba(239, 239, 239, 1)"/></fill><border color="rgba(217, 217, 217, 1)" lineJoin="miter" miterLimit="10"/><content fontSize="16" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(31, 35, 41, 1)" autoFit="shape-auto-fit"><p textAlign="center"><strong><span fontSize="14">H2（下半年）</span></strong></p><p textAlign="center"><strong><span color="rgba(31, 35, 41, 1)" backgroundColor="rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)" fontSize="12" fontFamily="思源黑体" italic="false" strikethrough="false" underline="false">依托全新技术地基，聚焦全链路风控加固与极简用户体验打造，以技术驱动业务，保障支付业务平稳落地与合规增长。</span></strong></p></content></shape><shape width="403.9999999999997" height="58" topLeftX="51.55097533847944" topLeftY="190.77035433070873" presetHandlers="0" type="rect" id="bwW"><fill><fillColor color="rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.08)"/></fill><content fontSize="16" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(31, 35, 41, 1)"/></shape><icon width="22.54883720930231" height="24" topLeftX="62.82539394313061" topLeftY="207.77035433070873" iconType="iconpark/Hardware/server.svg" id="bJw"><fill><fillColor color="rgba(59, 130, 246, 1)"/></fill></icon><shape width="357.0232558139532" height="54" topLeftX="93.83004510592127" topLeftY="194.77035433070873" type="text" id="bJX"><content fontSize="16" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(31, 35, 41, 1)" lineSpacing="multiple:1.2"><p lineSpacing="multiple:1.2"><strong><span color="rgba(31, 41, 55, 1)" fontSize="14" fontFamily="思源黑体">01 后端架构核心重构：</span></strong><span color="rgba(75, 85, 99, 1)" fontSize="13" fontFamily="思源黑体">全面废弃旧版PHP架构，迁移至Java治理体系，实现接口标准化与资源弹性调度，彻底消除非标接口与共用Token的安全隐患。</span></p></content></shape><shape width="403.9999999999997" height="58" topLeftX="51.55097533847944" topLeftY="258.7703543307087" presetHandlers="0" type="rect" id="bJC"><fill><fillColor color="rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.08)"/></fill><content fontSize="16" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(31, 35, 41, 1)"/></shape><icon width="22.54883720930231" height="24" topLeftX="62.82539394313061" topLeftY="275.7703543307087" iconType="iconpark/Hardware/phone.svg" id="bJq"><fill><fillColor color="rgba(59, 130, 246, 1)"/></fill></icon><shape width="357.0232558139532" height="54" topLeftX="93.83004510592127" topLeftY="262.7703543307087" type="text" id="bJN"><content fontSize="16" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(31, 35, 41, 1)" lineSpacing="multiple:1.2"><p lineSpacing="multiple:1.2"><strong><span color="rgba(31, 41, 55, 1)" fontSize="14" fontFamily="思源黑体">02 App跨平台架构升级：</span></strong><span color="rgba(75, 85, 99, 1)" fontSize="13" fontFamily="思源黑体">采用Flutter实现跨平台复用，大幅降低多端维护成本，并全面打通2FA（双因素认证）与SSO统一登录能力。</span></p></content></shape><shape width="403.9999999999997" height="58" topLeftX="51.550975338479724" topLeftY="326.77035433070864" presetHandlers="0" type="rect" id="bJb"><fill><fillColor color="rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.08)"/></fill><content fontSize="16" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(31, 35, 41, 1)"/></shape><icon width="22.54883720930231" height="24" topLeftX="62.82539394313089" topLeftY="343.77035433070864" iconType="iconpark/Travel/globe.svg" id="bJj"><fill><fillColor color="rgba(59, 130, 246, 1)"/></fill></icon><shape width="357.0232558139532" height="54" topLeftX="93.83004510592156" topLeftY="330.77035433070864" type="text" id="bJt"><content fontSize="16" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(31, 35, 41, 1)" lineSpacing="multiple:1.2"><p lineSpacing="multiple:1.2"><strong><span color="rgba(31, 41, 55, 1)" fontSize="14" fontFamily="思源黑体">03 海外Web端标准化建设：</span></strong><span color="rgba(75, 85, 99, 1)" fontSize="13" fontFamily="思源黑体">从0到1搭建标准化海外账号中心，采用分步式极简表单设计优化登录注册流程，有效降低用户操作流失率。</span></p></content></shape><shape width="403.9999999999997" height="58" topLeftX="51.55097533849739" topLeftY="399.77035433070864" presetHandlers="0" type="rect" id="bJn"><fill><fillColor color="rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.08)"/></fill><content fontSize="16" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(31, 35, 41, 1)"/></shape><icon width="22.54883720930231" height="24" topLeftX="62.825393943148555" topLeftY="416.77035433070864" iconType="iconpark/Safe/shield.svg" id="bJM"><fill><fillColor color="rgba(59, 130, 246, 1)"/></fill></icon><shape width="357.0232558139532" height="54" topLeftX="98.5277195245439" topLeftY="403.77035433070864" type="text" id="bJV"><content fontSize="16" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(31, 35, 41, 1)" lineSpacing="multiple:1.2"><p lineSpacing="multiple:1.2"><strong><span color="rgba(31, 41, 55, 1)" fontSize="14" fontFamily="思源黑体">04 全链路安全体系破局：</span></strong><span color="rgba(31, 41, 55, 1)" fontSize="12" fontFamily="思源黑体" bold="false">安全能力从无到有，</span><span color="rgba(75, 85, 99, 1)" fontSize="13" fontFamily="思源黑体">上线非授信设备登录强制二次验证机制，实现2FA全端覆盖，构建安全模型底座（设备环境检测）能力（已完成65%）。</span></p></content></shape><shape width="408.4733525299638" height="58" topLeftX="495.28970887188655" topLeftY="191.7703543307087" presetHandlers="0" type="rect" id="bwf"><fill><fillColor color="rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.08)"/></fill><content fontSize="16" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(31, 35, 41, 1)"/></shape><icon width="22.798512699346816" height="24" topLeftX="506.68896522155995" topLeftY="208.7703543307087" iconType="iconpark/Safe/protection.svg" id="bJo"><fill><fillColor color="rgba(16, 185, 129, 1)"/></fill></icon><shape width="360.97645107299127" height="54" topLeftX="538.0369201831619" topLeftY="195.7703543307087" type="text" id="bJS"><content fontSize="16" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(31, 35, 41, 1)" lineSpacing="multiple:1.2"><p lineSpacing="multiple:1.2"><strong><span color="rgba(31, 41, 55, 1)" fontSize="14" fontFamily="思源黑体">01 风控体系全面加固：</span></strong><span color="rgba(75, 85, 99, 1)" fontSize="13" fontFamily="思源黑体">部署业界级二次验证能力，强化第三方账号安全能力，建立全维度风控规则库，严厉打击伪冒账号与盗刷行为。</span></p></content></shape><shape width="408.4733525299638" height="58" topLeftX="495.2897088718863" topLeftY="259.77035433070864" presetHandlers="0" type="rect" id="bJU"><fill><fillColor color="rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.08)"/></fill><content fontSize="16" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(31, 35, 41, 1)"/></shape><icon width="22.798512699346816" height="24" topLeftX="506.6889652215597" topLeftY="276.7703543307086" iconType="iconpark/Hands/fingerprint.svg" id="bJd"><fill><fillColor color="rgba(16, 185, 129, 1)"/></fill></icon><shape width="360.97645107299127" height="54" topLeftX="538.0369201831617" topLeftY="263.7703543307086" type="text" id="bJv"><content fontSize="16" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(31, 35, 41, 1)" lineSpacing="multiple:1.2"><p lineSpacing="multiple:1.2"><strong><span color="rgba(31, 41, 55, 1)" fontSize="14" fontFamily="思源黑体">02 Passkey无密码验证创新：</span></strong><span color="rgba(75, 85, 99, 1)" fontSize="13" fontFamily="思源黑体">引入生物识别与端云并行风控，实现无感身份确认，在保障极高安全性的同时，大幅降低支付环节的账号验证流失率。</span></p></content></shape><shape width="408.4733525299638" height="58" topLeftX="495.28970887188655" topLeftY="326.77035433070864" presetHandlers="0" type="rect" id="bwB"><fill><fillColor color="rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.08)"/></fill><content fontSize="16" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(31, 35, 41, 1)"/></shape><icon width="22.798512699346816" height="24" topLeftX="506.68896522155995" topLeftY="343.77035433070864" iconType="iconpark/Charts/data-screen.svg" id="bJJ"><fill><fillColor color="rgba(16, 185, 129, 1)"/></fill></icon><shape width="360.97645107299127" height="54" topLeftX="538.0369201831619" topLeftY="330.77035433070864" type="text" id="bJm"><content fontSize="16" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(31, 35, 41, 1)" lineSpacing="multiple:1.2"><p lineSpacing="multiple:1.2"><strong><span color="rgba(31, 41, 55, 1)" fontSize="14" fontFamily="思源黑体">03 数据互联与精细化运营：</span></strong><span color="rgba(75, 85, 99, 1)" fontSize="13" fontFamily="思源黑体">整合行为、商品、售后全量数据，搭建账号数据看板，实现用户属性与支付、订阅等业务场景的深度联动与智能运营。</span></p></content></shape><shape width="408.4733525299638" height="58" topLeftX="495.2897088718863" topLeftY="399.77035433070864" presetHandlers="0" type="rect" id="bJg"><fill><fillColor color="rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.08)"/></fill><content fontSize="16" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(31, 35, 41, 1)"/></shape><icon width="22.798512699346816" height="24" topLeftX="506.6889652215597" topLeftY="416.77035433070864" iconType="iconpark/Safe/balance-two.svg" id="bJe"><fill><fillColor color="rgba(16, 185, 129, 1)"/></fill></icon><shape width="360.97645107299127" height="54" topLeftX="538.0369201831617" topLeftY="403.77035433070864" type="text" id="bJE"><content fontSize="16" fontFamily="思源黑体" color="rgba(31, 35, 41, 1)" lineSpacing="multiple:1.2"><p lineSpacing="multiple:1.2"><strong><span color="rgba(31, 41, 55, 1)" fontSize="14" fontFamily="思源黑体">04 隐私合规与体验优化：</span></strong><span color="rgba(75, 85, 99, 1)" fontSize="13" fontFamily="思源黑体">完善全链路数据合规采集与日志审计，完成Google Play合规上架，优化支持单业务独立注销的精细化销户体验通，全面满足隐私监管要求。</span></p></content></shape></data><note id="bbr"><content/></note></slide>